casebody.data:
No. 09-1404. Teamsters Local Union No. 523, Petitioner v. National Labor Relations Board, et al. 562 U.S. 801, 131 S. Ct. 109,

178 L. Ed. 2d 1,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 6557. October 4, 2010.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit for further consideration in light of New Process Steel, L.P. v. NLRB, 560 U.S. 674, 130 S. Ct. 2635, 177 L. Ed. 2d 162 (2010).

Same case below, 590 F.3d 849.
